  "detailed_description": "Clodhoppers is an online and local single/multiplayer brawler designed around quick games and big laughs. All the artwork is created using clay models and stop motion animation to give a unique aesthetic. It's lead by the creator of Platypus, Anthony Flack, and is the spiritual successor to Cletus Clay. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features:<br />\r\n- Multiplayer brawling for up to 4 players<br />\r\n- Stop-motion animated clay characters<br />\r\n- Pickup'n'play controls<br />\r\n- Hicks (and soon... cows... and then... thieving alien scum)<br />\r\n- Multiple controller support",
